## What Each Stage Does
```
Stage 1: Start Grid    → docker compose up
Stage 2: Checkout      → pull from GitHub
Stage 3: Build         → mvn clean install
Stage 4: Smoke Tests   → quick sanity check
Stage 5: Regression    → full test suite
Stage 6: Stop Grid     → docker compose down
Stage 7: Publish       → HTML report in Jenkins

Post:
→ Always: archive reports
→ Success: green email
→ Failure: red email with logs